OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784281689
OL,3,CMP urges Government to press US to
OL,4,Creopen case after dad shoots daughter
OL,6,FAn MP has called for the Government to
OL,7,Fput pressure on the authorities in
OL,8,FTexas to reopen the case of a British
OL,9,Fwoman who was shot dead by her father
OL,10,Fin the US.
OL,12,FLucy Harrison, from Warrington, was
OL,13,Fkilled in January 2025 at her father's
OL,14,Fhome near Dallas, after they had
OL,15,Fargued about US President Donald Trump.
OL,17,FA grand jury in Collin County decided
OL,18,Fagainst indicting Kris Harrison, and
OL,19,Fno criminal case was brought against
OL,20,Fhim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
