OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784281689
OL,3,CMP urges Government to press US to
OL,4,Creopen case after dad shoots daughter
OL,6,FHowever, earlier this year an inquest
OL,7,Finto the 23-year-old fashion buyer's
OL,8,Fdeath found that Mr Harrison had
OL,9,F"recklessly" shot his daughter in the
OL,10,Fchest while they were both in his
OL,11,Fbedroom.
OL,13,FThe court heard he had been drinking
OL,14,Fon the day he shot Lucy. He had
OL,15,Fpurportedly taken her into the room to
OL,16,Fshow her his gun.
OL,18,FSenior coroner for Cheshire Jacqueline
OL,19,FDevonish said his actions had amounted
OL,20,Fto unlawful killing on the grounds of
OL,21,Fgross negligence manslaughter.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
