OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784281689
OL,3,CMP urges Government to press US to
OL,4,Creopen case after dad shoots daughter
OL,6,FLabour MP for Warrington South, Sarah
OL,7,FHall, told an end-of-term debate in
OL,8,Fthe House of Commons that she wanted
OL,9,Fofficials and ministers to encourage
OL,10,Fauthorities in Texas to reopen or
OL,11,Freconsider Lucy's case.
OL,13,FThe MP said: "She was in her father's
OL,14,Fhome, somewhere she should have been
OL,15,Fsafe."
OL,26,@uD@NOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784281689
OL,3,CMP urges Government to press US to
OL,4,Creopen case after dad shoots daughter
OL,6,FSarah Hall said Lucy's family,
OL,7,Fincluding her mother Jane Coates, and
OL,8,Fher boyfriend Sam Littler who was in
OL,9,Fthe house when she was shot, were not
OL,10,Fgiven "adequate support" from the
OL,11,FForeign Office, including information
OL,12,Fon how the Texas legal system works.
OL,14,FShe said: "The Prosper Police
OL,15,FDepartment investigated Lucy's death
OL,16,Fas a possible criminal negligent
OL,17,Fhomicide, but the case was later
OL,18,Fconsidered by a grand jury in Texas
OL,19,Fand no criminal charges were brought.
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@XO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784281689
OL,3,CMP urges Government to press US to
OL,4,Creopen case after dad shoots daughter
OL,6,F"The gun had simply gone off. When the
OL,7,Fevidence was later examined at Lucy's
OL,8,Finquest in Cheshire, the conclusion
OL,9,Fwas very different.
OL,11,F"The senior coroner found that Lucy
OL,12,Fhad been unlawfully killed, the senior
OL,13,Fcoroner for Cheshire told the court
OL,14,Fthat Lucy's father's actions on the
OL,15,Fday of her death were truly
OL,16,Fexceptionally bad and reprehensible,
OL,17,Fso as to amount to her death, and she
OL,18,Frejected the account that the gun had
OL,19,Fsimply gone off."
OL,26,@sD@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
