PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784281689
OL,3,CMP urges Government to press US to
OL,4,Creopen case after dad shoots daughter
OL,6,FShe added that Lucy's family wanted
OL,7,Fthe coroner's findings to be taken
OL,8,Fseriously and fully re-examined by the
OL,9,FUS authorities.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
