OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1784281689
OL,3,CMP urges Government to press US to
OL,4,Creopen case after dad shoots daughter
OL,6,FSarah Hall said: "I implore the
OL,7,FGovernment to use every channel it has
OL,8,Fto press the relevant authorities in
OL,9,FTexas to reopen or formally reconsider
OL,10,FLucy's case, and to stand alongside a
OL,11,FBritish family to ensure that the
OL,12,Ffindings of a British court are
OL,13,Fproperly considered, and as a matter
OL,14,Fof urgency to ensure the FCDO in
OL,15,Ffuture does more to support the
OL,16,Ffamilies of constituents murdered
OL,17,Fabroad."
OL,26,@nD@ROUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
